src:
Dawn (E'Dawn) is hurt in 'MONEY' MV teaser
02 Nov 2019, 23:33 by jennywill
Dawn is ready to show it all in his latest teasers for his debut release under P-Nation titled 'Money'.
The MV teaser shows an edgy and aesthetic look just like the teasers did. Dawn is definitely taking steps to show off his newfound artistry in his upcoming release, and fans are excited to see what he has to offer.
Check out the teaser above and stay tuned for more updates!
